      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care typically reserved for private collections. Mechanically unassailable and aesthetically perfect, this specimen offers a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire a showroom-quality asset.",
      "price": 47500.0,
